  <http://syn.org/node> <http://syn.org/ccdi/molecular_test>;
  <http://syn.org/type> "string";
  <http://syn.org/isCDE> 6142508 .

<http://syn.org/ccdi/molecular_test/second_gene_symbol> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label>
